  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13084985/seefeld-cross-country-skiing.jpg" alt="crosscountryhero" data-udi="umb://media/47ba418b0b314b89ac706c3952aea1a9" /></p>
<p>Soak in that scenery - Cross-country skiing is easy to learn as well as a great way to enjoy the scenery at your own pace. It's a gentler way to take in the fresh pine scents, the sparkle of frozen lakes and the sheer tranquillity and beauty of winter in the mountains.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1e6f5e817a4f4af3b851984b9c3fa71c}" title="Deals" class="c-btn">Ski holiday deals</a></p>
<h2>Best cross-country skiing in Europe</h2>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/ed82c0b90e2d48e384f4fc0638e8018a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ed82c0b90e2d48e384f4fc0638e8018a}" title="Seefeld">Seefeld</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img style="width: 500px; height: 238.69047619047618px;" src="/media/1714/paesaggio-apt-24-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=238.69047619047618" alt="SeefeldCrossCountry" data-udi="umb://media/517fe871e4114b67983dfc76d26fb749" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ed82c0b90e2d48e384f4fc0638e8018a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ed82c0b90e2d48e384f4fc0638e8018a}" title="Seefeld">Seefeld</a> is Austria's leading resort and one of the largest cross-country areas in Europe, with 279km of trails. From nursery areas to Olympic tracks - Seefeld's trails offer something for everyone. With many trails being snow sure due to the use of snow cannons and free use of the trails with the Seefeld guest card, it really is a cross-country paradise.</p>
<ul>
<li>The trails link 5 different villages: Seefeld, Leutasch, Mosern, Reith and Scharnitz</li>
<li>154km of classic trails</li>
<li>Grades: easy, medium, difficult</li>
<li>Height difference: 1180 - 1550 km</li>
<li>Specialised cross country ski school</li>
<li>A 3km trail is floodlit Monday to Friday</li>
<li>Seefeld has twice hosted Winter Olympics</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria" class="c-btn">Austria ski holidays</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria">Austria</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 400px; height: 200px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13088687/cross-country-skiing.jpg?width=400&amp;height=200" alt="MayrhofenCrossCountry" data-udi="umb://media/9e0d1370e86e4a448ed192a052edfe80" /></p>
<p>Not the largest of of cross-country trail offerings, but certainly one of the most well maintained. Mayrhofen resort has 40km of perfectly groomed trails to explore. Known to have good snow conditions throughout the season, you will usually find a minimum density of 30cm of snow. </p>
<ul>
<li>Longest trail is 25km long from Mayrhofen to Zell am Ziller</li>
<li>There are a total of 16 trails in the vicinity of Mayrhofen</li>
<li>For more experienced cross-country skiers high-altitude trail Schwendberg is a little tougher but the panoramic views are reward enough</li>
<li>One of the longest trails is nearly 9km, near Tux (the rear of Zillertal)</li>
<li>There is a 1.5km floodlit trail for nigh-time cross-country</li>
<li>Grades: easy, medium, difficult</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7cc7c659d5214aa9b4d7bed936a721bb}" title="Austria" class="c-btn">Austria ski holidays</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77}" title="Soldeu">Soldeu</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra">Andorra</a></h3>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img style="width: 500px; height: 238.69047619047618px;" src="/media/13051866/austria_kitzbuhel-alps_st-johann_cross-country-skiing.jpg?width=500&amp;height=238.69047619047618" alt="SoldeuCrossCountry" data-udi="umb://media/40e82648a6384706b278374fc1d74e32" /></p>
<p>One of the smaller cross-country ski areas, but therefore one of the quieter cross-country ski areas is Soldeu - making it perfect for beginners or skiers going at their own, leisurely pace.</p>
<ul>
<li>The longest trail in Soldeu is an extensive 44m loop and will take even a proficient cross-country skier about 5 hours</li>
<li>There are however plenty of shorter trails, even under a mile that are very easy to manage</li>
<li>The trails near Soldeu sit at a high-altitude - on average at 2,210m</li>
<li>Spend a day to visit Naturland, this adventure park has 15km of dedicated cross-country only ski trails</li>
<li>Grades: easy, medium, difficult</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra" class="c-btn">Andorra ski holidays</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77}" title="Soldeu">St Moritz</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/043e5aa9497c411db243e21ed0a5049b}" title="Andorra">Switzerland</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 500px; height: 238.69px; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/media/13066469/cross-country-in-davos.jpg?width=500&amp;height=238.69047619047618" alt="SwitzerlandCrossCountry" data-udi="umb://media/eaee2fc099774293af08c9cf04cd3624" /></p>
<p>With a vast expanse of cross-country ski trails, St Moritz should b top of the list for your next cross-country skiing holiday. Offering 230km of ski trails that meander throughout the area. </p>
<ul>
<li>Try the impressive and full day trail from Maloja to S-chanf - a full 42km</li>
<li>A range of views are on offer here, from tree-laden forests, frozen lakes to valley views</li>
<li>St Moritz is part of the largest cross-country ski network in Switzerland</li>
<li>The trails range from easy, moderate to difficult - meaning there is a trail for everyone </li>
<li>The trails are slightly longer on average, with the shortest being 2km</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn">Switzerland ski holidays</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13065811/6-1.jpg" alt="CrossCountrySkiing" data-udi="umb://media/8f7000d20c6a446eb599c44a7153a2e1" /></p>
