<h4 style="text-align: left;">Learn to Cross-country ski:</h4>
<p>Our exciting <strong>'Learn to Cross-country ski'</strong> beginner packages are available in:</p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/ed82c0b90e2d48e384f4fc0638e8018a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ed82c0b90e2d48e384f4fc0638e8018a}" title="Seefeld">Seefeld</a> </li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a></li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77}" title="Soldeu">Soldeu</a> </li>
</ul>
<p>Packages include: tuition and ski &amp; boot hire, and are a great way to try out this popular sport. Contact our <a data-udi="umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193}" title="Contact Us">Reservations Team</a> to learn more.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2><img src="/media/13070012/yllas_filler14.jpg" alt="CrossCountryLapland" data-udi="umb://media/c53e6ba1962f4d769e303ff84a88e584" /></h2>
<h2>Cross-country skiing in <a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">Lapland</a>:</h2>
<p>We also offer skiing holidays to Lapland and it is worth considering here if you are an avid cross-country skier or keen to learn. Lapland has huge dedicated areas to this winter sport.</p>
<p>Sitting above the arctic circle, cross-country skiing in Lapland is a magical experience, with nature at it's finest. </p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/ski-holidays/resorts/hotels/item476/levi/">Levi</a> </strong>- Simply the best for all ability levels with refreshment huts and unlimited trails. Levi offers specific trails for cross-country skiing, depending on your level so you can ski to your ability whilst enjoying your surroundings.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka"><strong>Saariselkä</strong></a> - A cross-country enthusiast's paradise with mile after mile of well-marked trails through scenic Arctic wilderness. Saariselka is a very special cross-country skiing destination, with 200km of trails, 34km of which are illuminated.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas"><strong>Ylläs</strong></a> - Excellent for all ability levels with refreshment huts and trails in wonderful scenery. Yllas offers 330km of well maintained trails, that are easy to access for true cross-skier beginners.</li>
</ul>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays" class="c-btn">View Lapland</a></p>
</div>
</div>
